snippet.title: MLB 09 The Show (PS2, last-gen version) - Gameplay
snippet.description: A full game of MLB 09: The Show, a baseball video game by San Diego Studio. This is from the PlayStation 2 version of the game for a game that was also released on PS3. San Diego Padres at Chicago Cubs.
